title: Starting le Youtube channel! Could use with opinions for my first vid!

embed.description: Yorick walks into a bar. There is no counter. Except a Trynd. League of Legends, Undertale, and Underpants all belong to their original owners and I do not own any of their content. I simply mish-mash parts of them together for the laughs and what not. Chook's Channel:

body:
Tell me what you guys think about it! I'd love any kind of feedback and some requests for champ combinations or games to play! (Depends if i have the champs or games though XP)

I'll be making some more soon enough when i don't lose by a landslide XP I will post losses, but not massive ones (Since I can get a bit salty tbh ^_^; So that needs working on)
